   TRAVEL-COSTARICA _ ALAJUELA, Costa Rica _ How did I get myself
into this? Here I am, pedaling a 21-speed ``hybrid'' bike up and
down the mountains of Costa Rica. I'm bouncing along jagged roads
and squeezing the hand brakes at every downhill turn. It sounded
like a good idea at the time. . . . (Fuchs, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
