<P>
   TRUMP-RESORT _ PALM BEACH _ What's an ocean-to-lake club without
so much as a lounge chair on the beach? It's Donald Trump's
Mar-a-Lago Club. Hardly seems worth the $75,000 membership fee if
members have to tote their own beach chairs. Trump wants to change
that. He has plans to build a 100-foot long seaside pool, 14
cabanas with showers, a snack bar, bathrooms and two decorative
fountains on the club's 360 feet of beachfront. (O'Meilia, Palm
Beach Post) MOVED.
