<P>
   BBN-HOMER-CONFLICT _ Suddenly, all that's clear is the conflict
within. I want McGwire to have the eventual record, whatever it may
be, because he performed so valiantly in running down both Ruth and
Maris for the home fans at the end of a Cardinals homestand. I want
Sosa to have it because he didn't begrudge McGwire the moment.
(George, Palm Beach Post) MOVED.
</P>
<P>
   BOX-HOLYFIELD _ ATMORE, Ala. _ Evander Holyfield's birthplace is
this town near the Florida border. He moved to Atlanta as a young
child and doesn't talk much about it, even though his father and
other relatives live there. Though he's been gone three decades,
some locals remember him going around at age 3 with his fists
clenched, challenging someone to box. (Levine, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution) ETA 8 p.m. ET.
