Tuesday he is disappointed with President Clinton's admission to
having an ``inappropriate relationship'' with former White House
intern Monica Lewinsky. He also called for a speedy resolution to
the matter for the good of the country, and said even if Clinton
maintains the presidential helm, he will be ineffective for the
next two years. Preston
