representatives from several national farmer organizations traveled
to Washington anxious to make sure that their lawmakers did not
forget about the problems back home. Brown
</P>
<P>
   VIRGIN ISLANDS -- PR. A tight legislative schedule and a lack of
consensus in the Senate have combined to spell doom for legislation
authorizing a referendum on the future of Puerto Rico. Williams
</P>
