first in-house production by Garry Marshall's Falcon Theatre,
Burbank.
</P>
<P>
   ``The Woody Guthrie Show'': An annual tribute to America's
populist troubadour, Sept. 27, Will Geer Theatricum Botanicum.
</P>
<P>
   ``Tainted Blood'': A combination drawing-room comedy, detective
story and gothic horror tale, Oct. 2-Nov. 22, The Road Theatre
Company, Lankershim Arts Center, North Hollywood.
</P>
