<HEADLINE>
`THE PROFESSOR AND THE MADMAN': SEARCHING FOR A LIFE, HE FOUND THE
LANGUAGE 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (SUBS to add photo note; no other changes)   (Editors: publication notes at end of review)  
(ART ADV: Photo for use with this story is being sent to NYT photo
clients. Non-subscribers may make individual purchase by calling
(888) 603-1036 or (888) 346-9867.) 
 (bl)  
 By RICHARD BERNSTEIN   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service    
<TEXT>
<P>
   The subtitle of Simon Winchester's new book, ``The Professor and
the Madman: A Tale of Murder, Insanity and the Making of the Oxford
