<P>
   CALJOBS-WILLJUMP (Los Angeles) _ Led by a surging service
sector, California's employment will mushroom about 50 percent
during the first two decades of the next century as new job seekers
flock to the state, says a widely watched economic forecast. By
Gregory J. Wilcox.
