<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-RUSSIA-ECONOMY-BOS </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
PRIMAKOV PRESSED FOR ECONOMIC BAILOUT PLAN 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (i and f coding)   (For use by New York Times News Service clients)  
 By DAVID FILIPOV  
 c.1998 The Boston Globe  
 
<TEXT>
