<HEADLINE>
BUSINESS TRAVEL: COMPETING STRATEGIES; CROWDED SKIES 
</HEADLINE>
  (Duplication warning: Also filed in ``f'' category) 
(mk) 
 By JANE L. LEVERE   
 c.1998 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
